g.title: quoteParty
g.text: Common ID between the FSPs for the quote object, decided by the Payer FSP
Specifies the type of party this row relates to; typically PAYER or PAYEE
Specifies the type of identifier used to identify this party e.g. MSISDN, IBAN etc...
Reference to the resolved FSP ID (if supplied/known). If not an error will be reported
The role this Party is playing in the transaction
The type of financial entry this Party is presenting
Trading currency pertaining to the party amount

g.title: quote
g.text: Common ID (decided by the Payer FSP) between the FSPs for the future transaction object
This is part of the transaction initiator
This is part of the transaction initiator type
This is part of the transaction scenario
This is part of the transaction type that contains the elements- balance of payment
This is part of the transaction type sub scenario as defined by the local scheme
This is part of the transaction type that contains valid elements for - Amount Type
Trading currency pertaining to the Amount
